<div class="separator"></div> </div> </div>         <h2>Сентябрь 2017 г.</h2>       <div class="block-border card-block expert-review"> <div id="review-861987" class="review-861987" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">         <div class="rback">    <div class="group-review"> <div class="with-pad event-header"> <div style="position:relative;"> <div class="group-actionbar"> <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2017-09-27 04:17:58">        </div>              <span class="label-orange review-expert">Рецензия эксперта</span> <span class="expert-sign">Шмэксперт</span>  <div class="group-user-date" style="margin-bottom:0px;line-height:22px;"> <div class="login-hide"> <a href="/reader/TibetanFox" title="TibetanFox"><div class="event-user-avatar expert" style="background-image: url(https://j.livelib.ru/userpic/TibetanFox/60x60/189a/TibetanFox.jpg);"></div></a> <div class="group-login-date" style="vertical-align: middle;"> <div class="expert-login-wrapper"> <a class="a-login-black expert-login" href="/reader/TibetanFox" title="TibetanFox"><span itemprop="author">TibetanFox</span></a> </div>  написал(а) <a class="a-login-black" href="/review/861987-iphuck-10-viktor-pelevin">рецензию на книгу</a><br> <a href="/book/1002586414-iphuck-10-viktor-pelevin" title="iPhuck 10">iPhuck 10</a> автора <a href="/author/2355-viktor-pelevin">Виктор Пелевин</a>  <br> <span class="date-topright">   <a title="Рецензия на книгу &laquo;iPhuck 10&raquo;" href="/review/861987-iphuck-10-viktor-pelevin"><span class="date">27&nbsp;сентября&nbsp;2017&nbsp;г., 04:17</span></a>   </span> </div> </div> <div class="clear"></div> </div>
 </div> </div> <div class="backgr-block review"> <div class="card-block-text with-pad" style="min-height: 300px;border-top: 1px solid #D8D8D8;">             <div class="carousel-scifi-books book-cover smaller-margin smaller-margin" style="display:inline-block;margin-right:24px;">  <div class="cover-wrapper">  <a href="/book/1002586414-iphuck-10-viktor-pelevin" title="Виктор Пелевин - iPhuck 10"><img src="https://j.livelib.ru/boocover/1002586414/140x220/3b95/Viktor_Pelevin__iPhuck_10.jpg" alt="Виктор Пелевин - iPhuck 10" title="Виктор Пелевин - iPhuck 10" width="140" style="min-width:140px; min-height:220px; background-color: #ffffff;"/></a> <div class="book-moreinfo-wrapper" id="book-moreinfo-1002586414-912936"> <div itemprop="itemReviewed" class="v-middle"> <a class="book-name" href="/book/1002586414-iphuck-10-viktor-pelevin" title="Виктор Пелевин - iPhuck 10">iPhuck 10</a> <a class="book-author" href="/author/2355" title="Виктор Пелевин">Виктор Пелевин</a> </div> </div> <span class="book-moreinfo-btn" onclick="if($('book-moreinfo-1002586414-912936').isVisible()){$(this).removeClass('active');}else{$(this).addClass('active');};$('book-moreinfo-1002586414-912936').toggle();"></span> </div>  <div class="book-rating-scifi"> <span class="rating-book">  <span style="margin-right: 5px" class="rating-value stars-color-orange">3.9</span><span title="Рейтинг 3.865 (995  читателей, рейтинг ожидания 4.083)"><span class="r40-sc-orange"></span></span> </span> </div>  <div class="book-data">  <div id="xa-main-1002586414-0-491958" data-rand_id="491958" data-strict_edition_id="0" data-userbook_id="0" data-view_mode="popup" data-edition_id="1002586414" data-show="" data-show_extended="" class="userbook-container xa-main-1002586414-0" style="text-align: left;"><div style="position: relative;"><div style="position:relative"><span onclick="loginform_show();" style="margin-right: 0px;" class="userbook-button ub-full-button"><span class="userbook-button userbook-main-menu"><span class="